NK041(di)034:1: bla bslu 'chi bdag gi g.yul las rnam par rgyal
NK041(di)034:2: ba zhes snga 'gyur bka' ma'i gzhung las byung bar
NK041(di)034:3: grags pa'i lugs kyi phyag len ltar btang ba'i skabs
NK041(di)034:4: / yi dam gang byed kyi yar gzhi spyi ltar bshams pa'i mdun /
NK041(di)034:5: stegs bu'i dbus su nas dkar mo 'bo gang gi rgyab tu mda' dar sna snga btsugs /
NK041(di)034:6: de'i mdun du li sdir zhig gi nang bla lug
NK041(di)034:7: skye mched dod pa mar la bcos pa'i mtha' bskor
NK041(di)034:8: du / bla shing shug pa 'jag ma gcig /
NK041(di)034:15: bla nas sbyin bdag gi rtags 'byar /
NK041(di)034:16: tshon skud sna lnga rdor mdud byas pa la tshe gzungs kyi sngags kyis btab pa /
NK041(di)034:17: rin chen sna lnga bcas kyis bskor ba la steng nas sbyin bdag gi phor pas bkab /
NK041(di)034:18: de'i g.yas su sbyin bdag skyes pa yin na pho lug rkang pa g.yas pa dang /
NK041(di)034:19: bud med la mo lug gi rkang pa g.yon pa
NK041(di)034:20: ras dkar gyis dril nas tshon skud sna lngas bcings
NK041(di)034:21: pa / g.yon du snod gas chags med pa'i nang
NK041(di)034:22: bla mtsho mtshon byed chang gis gtams pa mar gyi
NK041(di)034:24: mdun du dbus su sbyin bdag gi 'dra glud la
NK041(di)034:25: zhwa gos lhwam gsum dri ma can dpal 'byor gyis
NK041(di)034:26: brgyan cing / glud rdzas gzhan yang spyi ltar bsham /
NK041(di)034:27: de'i g.yas su lha gzugs dkar po 'phyar zhing ngo
NK041(di)034:28: so mtho ba'i rnam pa can gyi mdun shwa dkar
NK041(di)034:29: po shwa mig drug pa gyen bstan dang /
NK041(di)034:30: g.yon du 'dre gzugs nag po bsnyal stabs kyis bzung
NK041(di)034:31: ba gdong smad pa'i rnam pa can gyi mdun du
NK041(di)034:32: shwa nag po mig gcig pa bzhag /
NK041(di)034:35: tshe thar tshe lug gzhon pa zhig nyin dang po
NK041(di)034:36: bdag bskyed tshar ba'i skabs tshe thar byas nas rang
NK041(di)034:39: phur chung lta bu'i bdag bskyed gang rung zhig sngon du 'gro bas /
NK041(di)034:40: gtor bsngo skong gso dang sbrel nas byed na rdor glu'i bar dkyus ltar bya /
NK041(di)034:41: de nas sngags drug gis glud yas mas byin gyis brlab /
NK041(di)034:42: bcom rol lha bsang bzhin byas la /
NK041(di)034:45: sangs rgyas rkang gnyis sogs sh+lo ka gcig la h'u mdzad sgra 'byin ma'i dbyangs rol /
NK041(di)034:46: dkon mchog bka' la man chad 'dur ma /
NK041(di)034:47: lha yang rgyal la 'dre yang pham //
NK041(di)034:48: zhes par tshig rol byas la bzhag /
NK041(di)034:49: rdor dril dang bcas h'u mdzad kyi rgyas /
NK041(di)034:51: rje btsun rtsa ba dang brgyud par bcas pa'i dpal
NK041(di)034:52: ldan bla ma dam pa rnams kyi bka' bden pa
NK041(di)034:53: dang / sangs rgyas kyi chos kyi dge 'dun gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK041(di)034:69: gzungs sngags kyi lha tshogs rnams kyi bka' bka' sdod chos skyong ma mo mkha' 'gro /
NK041(di)034:72: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i bka' bden pa dang /
NK041(di)034:73: bden pa yang dag pa dang /
NK041(di)034:74: bden pa chen po'i byin gyi rlabs kyis /
NK041(di)034:75: deng 'dir sbyin pa'i bdag po'i sku'i bla tshe srog
NK041(di)034:76: gsum sde brgyad ma rungs pa rnams kyis brkus pa
NK041(di)034:79: nyams chag tu gyur pa dang /
NK041(di)034:80: ban bon mthu bo che rnams kyis sngags dang /
NK041(di)034:82: bsam gtan gyi sbyor bas bla srog 'phrog pa thams cad skad cig /
NK041(di)034:84: yud tsam gyis dmigs pa'i rten 'di la mchis par gyur cig /
NK041(di)034:86: badz+ra am ku sha dzah badz+ra p+aa sha h'u /
NK041(di)034:88: badz+ra +aa be sha ya hoh zhes sgo ma bzhi'i rgyas /
NK041(di)034:89: bla srog tshe gsum bla gzugs dang 'od dang thig
NK041(di)034:90: le dang n+ri'i rnam pa gzi brjid 'bar bas bla
NK041(di)034:91: rten la thim par gyur pa'i dmigs pa dang /
NK041(di)034:92: tshe dpag med kyi gzungs ring bzlas pas gsol btab bcas lan gsum gyi bar du bya /
NK041(di)034:96: bla mtsho 'di la bla khug cig /
NK041(di)034:97: ces pa'i bar glu rgyal gyi gdangs /
NK041(di)034:99: bslu yang gcig la bslu yang gnyis //
NK041(di)034:103: skabs tshig rol dang bcas chem brdung gsum gyi mthar sum brdeg lan can /
NK041(di)034:106: khyed 'go ba'i lha la sogs la glu rgyal gyi gdangs /
NK041(di)034:108: dang po su dang su yi nas kang+ka d+ha ra'i dbyangs rol /
NK041(di)034:109: lan chags bu lon byang bar gyis //
NK041(di)034:111: rol mo bsgyur te dpang gzug gi dbyangs rol dang bcas /
NK041(di)034:112: gzhan yang gson bdud sogs nas /
NK041(di)034:115: rol mo'i mu nas chems brdung gi khongs su lha
NK041(di)034:116: glud dkar po dang srung ma'i gtor 'bul yod na
NK041(di)034:117: bcas khang steng du bskyal nas phyogs bzhir lha rgyal
NK041(di)034:119: 'dre glud nag po sbyin bdag gi glud bcas sgo
NK041(di)034:120: phyir bskyal nas 'dre lnga bdud gcod kyi phyogs su
NK041(di)034:121: btang / 'dre pham zhes dang gi shan 'ur rdo ki sgra sogs bya /
NK041(di)034:122: de nas sum brdeg lan can byas la skong gso'i 'phros rnams rdzogs par bya'o //
NK041(di)034:124: yon bdag gi bla rten gang rung gi mdun du kha gtad de bla lug chu dang bcas bzhag /
NK041(di)034:126: ha ri ni sa rdzab rdzab rdzub rdzub b+ha tra
NK041(di)034:127: slong slong n+ri khug dza dzah zhes pa'i sngags bzla
NK041(di)034:128: ba dang / dmod bor te bla lug bskor ba
NK041(di)034:129: lan gcig ma yin par kha bla rten la phyogs
NK041(di)034:130: te sdod na bla khug pa'i rtags su bshad /
NK041(di)034:133: snang zhing srid pa'i lha 'dre dang //
NK041(di)034:134: sogs bla bslu bcu gsum ma'i mjug nas 'byung bas gshegs gsol byed par gsungs /
NK041(di)034:135: tshar grangs byed na sngags drug phyag drug nas bzung ste bskyar zhing /
NK041(di)034:136: tshar grangs re re bzhin bla glud la changs bu /
NK041(di)034:139: de ltar dngos nyams su bla khug pa'i rtags dang /
NK041(di)034:140: bla lug rten la gdong phyogs pa sogs ma byung gi bar bya'o //
NK041(di)034:141: bla bslu 'di tshe sgrub kyi cha lag yin pas
NK041(di)034:142: bla ma zhi khro'i tshe sgrub lta bu tshe sgrub
NK041(di)034:143: gang rung gi bdag bskyed dang 'brel bar byas kyang
